aneously is a novel approach that has not been fully explored.\n\n**[Question 5] - What are the key components of my approach and results?**\nThe proposed methodology involves developing a novel UE method, Localized Neural Kernel (LNK), which uses GPs to extend existing GNN-based force fields. The method will be evaluated on a variety of molecular datasets, and its performance will be compared to existing UE methods in terms of accuracy and computational efficiency. The expected outcomes include a reliable UE method that can be integrated into GNN-based molecular force fields, leading to more accurate and efficient simulations.", role='assistant', tool_calls=None, function_call=None, provider_specific_fields=None)'.
